



Main Goal
---------

Since it will be designed for tools that the trader will use to make trading decisions in real time, it must be a system with clear priorities so that data is sent to the tools in nanoseconds.

    1. Sacrifice complexity for performance.
    2. Sacrifice space for performance.
    3. Sacrifice mental health for performance.


-----


Features
--------

* GraphQL server
* Websocket for realtime data streaming
* Soporte para multiples herramientas 